The evidence with the title 'Petroleum industry in Canada - Wikipedia ' says Petroleum production in Canada is a major industry which is important to the economy of North America . Canada has the third largest oil reserves in the world and is the world 's fifth largest oil producer and fourth largest oil exporter. In 2015 it produced an average of 621,610 cubic metres per day ( 3.9 mbbl/d) of crude oil  ... 
